Title: Compulsion
Plot: A serial killer strikes again, and the CSI team tries new technology using evidence from a prior killing.  They find a fingerprint belonging to Jesse Acheson, who becomes the prime suspect.  A boy confesses to the killing of his brother, but evidence suggests that he may not have committed the crime.
